title: Anna Shcherbakova and Evgenia Medvedeva talk figure skating
description: Figure skating has never been so breath-taking. Rising star Anna Shcherbekova and double Olympic silver medallist Evgenia Medvedeva break down why this Olympic season is one of the best we've ever witnessed.
